ChatReplay Configuration
 Should messages be automatically re-played on login?
   replayOnLogin
 If installed, should DiscordSRV messages be recorded?
   recordDiscordSRV
 Chat Buffer Options:
   bufferSize: How many of the most recent chat messages to store in total
   viewSize: How many messages to show players at once. Vanilla Minecraft Client has a history limit of around 100
 Messages
   Format of timestamp string. Do not use color / formatting codes.
   Format instructions: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/text/SimpleDateFormat.html
     timestampFormat
   Header and footer message of replay output
   Available variables: {{msgCount}}
     replayHeader
     replayFooter
   Formatting for single messages replayed
   Available variables: {{player}}, {{message}}, {{timestamp}}
     replayMsgFormat
     replayMsgHover
   Button to navigate chat history
      navigateHistoryButtonText);